<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />"I myself have anointed my king</para>

<para style="q1">on Zion, my holy mountain."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />I will announce a decree of Yahweh.</para>

<para style="q1">He said to me, "You are my son!</para>

<para style="q1">This day I have become your father.</para>
